uration", "text": "Front-end yields still sensitive to financial conditions reversal if risk assets rally sharply."}], "trade": {"legs": [{"instrument": "DGS2", "weight": -0.2}, {"instrument": "DGS6MO", "weight": 0.35}], "conviction": 0.35, "rationale": "Trim prior steepener size given softer conviction from balance sheet and stale inflation, but keep direction: less near-term tightening priced, labor loosening and financial conditions tightening dominate."}}

