ations despite flat labor/conditions readings."}, {"tag": "positioning", "text": "Small position size means little cost either way, but avoids overreacting to stale/low-conviction inputs."}], "trade": {"legs": [{"instrument": "DGS2", "weight": -0.01}, {"instrument": "DGS6MO", "weight": 0.01}], "conviction": 0.1, "rationale": "Trim prior slight front-end flattener toward flat given fading (not reversing) tightening case; near-zero size reflects genuine no-strong-view state."}}

